Insider Activity


Individual




Linda Kay Zecher



Ms. Linda K. Zecher is Independent Director at Hasbro, Inc., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Houghton Mifflin Harcourt Publishing Co., and President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Houghton Mifflin Harcourt Co. She is on the Board of Directors at Hasbro, Inc., Houghton Mifflin Harcourt Publishing Co., Houghton Mifflin Harcourt Co., John F. Kennedy Library Foundation, and Cradles To Crayons.
Ms. Zecher was previously employed as Vice President-Worldwide Public Sector by Microsoft Corp., Chief Executive Officer by Evolve Corp. Plc, Geophysicist by Texas Instruments, Incorporated., Head-Payroll Services System by Bank of America Corp., Senior Vice President by Oracle Corp., and Vice President-Sales & Marketing by PeopleSoft, Inc. She also served on the board at The Emily Couric Leadership Forum, Intelligence & National Security Alliance, and The Virginia Piedmont Technology Council.
She received her undergraduate degree from The Ohio State University.



