Latest NewsCompaniesMarketsEconomy & ForexCommoditiesInterest RatesBusiness LeadersFinance ProfessionalsCalendarSectors HomeAll newsMost read newsBusiness Leaders Biography


 
















Linda Kay Zecher

Age : 63Public asset : 2,944,473 USDLinked companies :  Hasbro, Inc. 





Summary 



Ms. Linda K. Zecher is on the Board of Directors at Hasbro, Inc., Houghton Mifflin Harcourt Publishing Co., Cradles To Crayons, John F. Kennedy Library Foundation, Choice Solutions, Inc. (Massachusetts) and Tom Snyder Productions, Inc. Ms. Zecher was previously employed as President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Houghton Mifflin Harcourt Co., Vice President-Worldwide Public Sector by Microsoft Corp., Head-Payroll Services System by Bank of America Corp., Chief Executive Officer by Evolve Corp. Plc, Senior Vice President by Oracle Corp., Vice President-Sales & Marketing by PeopleSoft, Inc., and Geophysicist by Texas Instruments Incorporated.She also served on the board at Intelligence & National Security Alliance, The Emily Couric Leadership Forum and The Virginia Piedmont Technology Council.She received her undergraduate degree from The Ohio State University.



